            <scopecontent id="aspace_02aaf88da141ff5a8771823b7a6f995f">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series contains the transcripts for each interview conducted by Johhn W. Cook and Heinrich Klotz with Louis I. Kahn.  An index that includes timestamps highlighting remarks relevant to the Yale Center for British Art and related correspondence has been placed at the end of the series.</p>
            </scopecontent>
            <arrangement id="aspace_70cb873b846287f2761b12528a194728">
               <head>Arrangement</head>
               <p>Material are arranged in chronological order by recording date, along with sides 1and 2 of the original audio cassettes.  Indices are arranged to provide an overview and introducion, followed by detailed information.</p>
            </arrangement>
